    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Neck-scarves worn with combat uniforms or service uniforms. Square or rectangular shape with closures at the back of the neck. Often in a regimental color with its emblem placed centrally.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
